data.description: If you are looking for an updated 3 bedroom 1 bath property with an easy commute to both Guntersville and Huntsville you have found it. Hardwood floors throughout, waterproof vinyl in the bathroom, and fresh paint throughout the house. This property sits just off of Highway 431 and is only 25-30 minutes from Hampton Cove and South Huntsville. Downtown Scottsboro is only 15-20 mins away.
